00:03:30.850 --> 00:03:40.510
they said try the macchiatone. It's a Venetian
specialty. It's

00:03:40.510 --> 00:03:44.420
basically think of it as in the middle between
a

00:03:44.420 --> 00:03:48.210
macchiato and a cappuccino. So macchiato with
a

00:03:48.210 --> 00:03:51.540
little bit more milk. So it's the perfect
combination of

00:03:51.540 --> 00:03:57.110
milk and espresso. And it's called different
things in

00:03:57.110 --> 00:03:59.471
different places in the world actually. So
several

00:03:59.471 --> 00:04:03.700
people have honed in on this concept. So I
had this drink. It

00:04:03.700 --> 00:04:06.190
was great. It was perfect. I went and I blogged
about

00:04:06.190 --> 00:04:09.630
it that day. Remember the days when people
used to

00:04:09.630 --> 00:04:12.560
express themselves in more than 140 characters.
