00:37:08.289 --> 00:37:11.690
the
only coffee book ever written that has a quote

00:37:11.690 --> 00:37:12.690
from Vint Cerf. [laughter]And I don't know
if

00:37:12.690 --> 00:37:25.190
you can read it. But it is really well-said.
And then, there's the World Barista Champion

00:37:25.190 --> 00:37:28.740
and the editor in chief of Barista Magazine.

00:37:28.740 --> 00:37:30.509
&gt;&gt;Male #13: No Italian.

