I'll take any -- you know, the one lesson

00:37:56.530 --> 00:37:58.970
that
I wanted to convey is the coffee world is

00:37:58.970 --> 00:38:02.810
moving really, really fast. Coffee is really
from the moment you take these cherries off

00:38:02.810 --> 00:38:04.943
the
tree until you dip them in the cup, the process

00:38:04.943 --> 00:38:08.309
is really
difficult. It's being pushed forward by a

00:38:08.309 --> 00:38:14.099
network of people in the world. It was really
amazing to be part of that community and see

00:38:14.099 --> 00:38:17.040
how things are changing. I really appreciate
the

00:38:17.040 --> 00:38:19.289
coffee that you have here at Google. [laughter]

00:38:19.289 --> 00:38:21.789
