[laughter]
&gt;&gt; So the most frequent question I get

00:41:17.369 --> 00:41:25.660
as I was writing this book is, "did you hear
about that cat that -- or the monkey that

00:41:25.660 --> 00:41:28.619
has
the thing". So there's a lot of misinformation

00:41:28.619 --> 00:41:31.740
about it. Yes, so it's called Kopi Luwak.
There's a civet cat

00:41:31.740 --> 00:41:35.670
that goes around -- what's interesting about
the civet cat is it actually goes in the fields.

00:41:35.670 --> 00:41:39.190
It
knows how to choose the right cherries. And

00:41:39.190 --> 00:41:45.839
then it digests -- eats the cherries. Comes
out from the other side and hopefully then

00:41:45.839 --> 00:41:55.529
cleans very thoroughly. And then, it's -- I
didn't like it. I had it. There's a section

00:41:55.529 --> 00:41:59.829
in the book about it. The -- what's happening
