00:41:59.829 --> 00:42:03.059
of
money doing this. So instead of having civet

00:42:03.059 --> 00:42:07.160
cats
run wild in the fields choosing the cherries,

00:42:07.160 --> 00:42:12.520
they put them in cages and they start feeding
them cherries and they charge the same prices.

00:42:12.520 --> 00:42:18.539
